lines.text: But, Honeybunch, sitting on eggs is sissy stuff!
Stop mumbling and sit on that egg!
Sssit on that egg or I'll...
Eeney, meeny, miney, mo. Where did that stupid little egg go? Oh, well, what's the difference? An egg is an egg.
Some people just can't seem to mind their own business.
All right, wise guy! Open up or else!
One more move out of you and I'll let 'em have it! What a stoop.
I should have listened to mother...
